      "choice": "Direct judge-minus-blind-human-pool mean offset (judge minus mean of 3 blind raters), from the '(LLM)' calibration rows (n=15 LLM generations) rather than the '(human)' rows, because the swap subset consists of LLM generations."
    },
    "notes": [
      "Subset = the n_cells_with_all_judges intersection from benchathon_inter_judge_agreement.json (258 generations).",
